com.googlecode.cqengine.persistence.support

Interface ObjectStore<O>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CollectionWrappingObjectStore, ConcurrentOnHeapObjectStore, FilteredObjectStore, SQLiteObjectStore

    public interface ObjectStore<O>
    An interface providing similar methods as Set, except the methods accept QueryOptions.

    This interface can thus wrap a standard on-heap Set, or an off-heap or disk implementation of a Set where the implementation can extract details of the persistence to use from the supplied query options.
